name: A Musical Tale / A5 Print / 5 x 8
description:
A portal is opened as an eerie tune intoxicates the woodland.

This is an inkjet print of my original pen drawing.

Printed on 225 gsm Somerset Enhanced Velvet paper that is made from 100% cotton fibres at St.Cuthberts Mill in Somerset and has a wonderfully subtle texture.

Paper size: A5 (148 x 210 mm), approx. 5 x 8

Each print has a white border and is signed on the front in pencil.

Your print will be carefully packaged in a protective cellophane sleeve before being shipped flat inside a hard backed envelope.

To see more of my work please visit www.scottnellis.com.

Thank you for visiting!



© 2013 Scott Nellis
